{
  "stem": "2578.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, because a lot-- a lot-- people, people died, I would say, because they ate so much the very first day when they got the food from the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I myself, I myself-- you see, if you open up a can of, let's say, conserved meat, and you ate it together with butter-- because everything, everything was, was not enough for us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we grabbed everything that, that we could at one time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whoever was conscious enough-- and, and, you know-- to understand in the condition that he is, that to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] discipline himself not to eat, maybe this helped him to survive.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And others just couldn't help themselves, which is understandable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Into some kind of a field hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, we were in this place a couple of weeks, maybe five, six weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were sent out into town, into town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a, a, a children's home for-- a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a German, a German, little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Dornhau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a, a-- it used to be a German children's home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was converted for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like this, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- you see--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After all, you know, it's about 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it is difficult to remember the exact dates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can only-- I can only remember the, the things that happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I remember, we were capable of walking around more or less normally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got different clothes, once we were there, we were sent out to this, to this home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I really don't-- I really don't remember the amount of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it must have been at least 150, maybe 200.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
